<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 17px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 34px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">各位考生：</p><p><br/></p><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 17px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">目前专升本录取工作已经完成，由于各位同学毕业高职院校正在审核2023届如期毕业学生毕业资格，教育厅也将根据审核结果，复核前期录取数据后下达最终录取库给我校，工作预计7月底完成，我校将在获取录取数据后第一时间邮寄通知书，特此告知！感谢您对我们工作的理解与支持!</section><p><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 17px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 34px; word-break: break-all; text-wrap